title: Joe Temperley discusses Harry Carney & Ellington's Band
fulltitle: Joe Temperley discusses Harry Carney & Ellington's Band
description:
This video is an excerpt from an interview that I conducted with baritone saxophonist Joe Temperley on October 26, 2014.

In this part of the interview, Joe Temperley discusses playing at Harry Carney's funeral and going on the road with Ellington's Band. 

This interview is part of the research that I completed on the life and career of jazz legend Joe Temperley. The project was funded by a generous Jazz Studies Grant through the University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill’s Department of Music.
